
  Statement 1 and Statement 2 is not the same because of the difference in having the "!"


If Statement 1

if(karel.canPickThing())                                    
{                                                        
    karel.turnRight();                               
} else {                                                   
    karel.turnLeft();                                
}                                                          





If Statement 2

if(!karel.canPickThing())
{                                                                          
    karel.turnLeft();
} else {                                                                                                                          
    karel.turnRight();
}                